OL,3,CLabour suffer losses and Reform make
OL,4,Cgains in early election results
OL,6,FThe Labour Party has lost control of
OL,7,Fmultiple local authorities in
OL,8,FEngland's local elections, with the
OL,9,Fparty suffering huge losses to Reform
OL,10,FUK as results trickle in.
OL,12,FReform's gains exceeded 270 seats when
OL,13,Fresults were in from 40 of the 136
OL,14,Fcouncils on Friday morning, while
OL,15,FLabour lost more than 200, including
OL,16,Fin its traditional northern heartlands.
OL,18,FThe Conservatives have also suffered
OL,19,Fseveral defeats, losing 61 seats,
OL,20,Fwhile the Liberal Democrats gained 29
OL,21,Fand the Green Party gained 23.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
