OL,3,CLabour suffer losses and Reform make
OL,4,Cgains in early election results
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FLabour lost eight local authorities as
OL,12,Fof 7.30am on Friday, including
OL,13,FSouthampton, Westminster, Tameside,
OL,14,FTamworth, Hartlepool, Redditch, Exeter
OL,15,Fand Wandsworth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
