OL,3,CLabour suffer losses and Reform make
OL,4,Cgains in early election results
OL,6,FLiberal Democrats deputy leader Daisy
OL,7,FCooper hailed her party's gains as a
OL,8,F"record-breaking winning streak".
OL,10,F"We are heading for our eighth set of
OL,11,Flocal election gains in a row and are
OL,12,Fon track to beat Labour and the
OL,13,FConservatives once again," Cooper said.
OL,15,F"I couldn't be more proud of our
OL,16,Fhardworking teams across the country,
OL,17,Fwho knocked on over three-and-a-half
OL,18,Fmillion doors to take the fight to
OL,19,FFarage and his politics of division."
OL,26,@{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
