OL,3,CLabour suffer losses and Reform make
OL,4,Cgains in early election results
OL,6,FSenior Conservative Sir James Cleverly
OL,7,Ftold ITV's Good Morning Britain the
OL,8,Fparty "always knew this was going to
OL,9,Fbe a difficult night" and described
OL,10,Fthe results as a "mixed picture".
OL,12,F"We recognise there is still work to
OL,13,Fdo, but Kemi (Badenoch) is setting out
OL,14,Fan agenda that is proving very popular
OL,15,Fon the doorstep," the shadow housing
OL,16,Fsecretary said.
OL,18,F"We are just a couple of years off the
OL,19,Fback of the worst election results
OL,20,Fwe've had in our history, and you're
OL,21,Fnot going to repair that overnight."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
