PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778328667
OL,3,CLabour suffer losses and Reform make
OL,4,Cgains in early election results
OL,6,FCleverly went on to say that Reform
OL,7,Fhad gained more votes in this election
OL,8,Fby making a "whole load of promises"
OL,9,Fthat they "keep failing to deliver".
OL,11,F"We always respect the choice of
OL,12,Fvoters because we respect democracy,
OL,13,Fbut we know that Reform will let them
OL,14,Fdown," Cleverly said.
OL,16,FMore than 5,000 seats were being voted
OL,17,Ffor on Thursday across 136 councils
OL,18,Facross England, alongside six local
OL,19,Fmayoral contests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
