OL,3,CLabour suffer losses and Reform make
OL,4,Cgains in early election results
OL,6,FScotland and Wales also went to the
OL,7,Fpolls, with results expected later on
OL,8,FFriday. All 129 seats were up for
OL,9,Felection at Holyrood, and Welsh voters
OL,10,Fhave been choosing 96 members of the
OL,11,FSenedd.
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
